description: Kanade is another one of the female characters. Kanade seems to have two sides to herself. The first night at the school, Tomo is attacked by Kanade, where she has one blue eye and one green eye and wears the outfit of a miko. The next day at school, Tomo confronts Kanade when she has two blue eyes. Kanade claims to have no memory of the previous night.
name: Takatsuki Kanade
